---
// Features section - All app features with clear benefit framing
---

<section class="features section" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="label label-coral">Features</span>
      <h2>Everything you need to stay consistent</h2>
      <p>Simple, powerful tools designed around one goal: keeping you accountable.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <!-- Core Features Row -->
      <div class="feature-card feature-large reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon-large">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Partner & Group Accountability</h3>
          <p>Pair with one partner or join a group of up to 8. Enable "All Accountable" mode where one miss resets everyone. Real social cost, real motivation.</p>
          <ul class="feature-bullets">
            <li>Partner mode: linked streaks</li>
            <li>Group mode: team accountability</li>
            <li>All Members Accountable option</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card feature-large reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon-large green">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Photo Proof Check-ins</h3>
          <p>Capture proof of completion with automatic watermarks showing date, time, and streak count. Or use honor-based check-ins for privacy. Your choice.</p>
          <ul class="feature-bullets">
            <li>Auto-watermarked photos</li>
            <li>Encrypted and private</li>
            <li>Honor-based option</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Standard Feature Cards -->
      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 2v4m0 12v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83m8.48 8.48l2.83 2.83M2 12h4m12 0h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83m8.48-8.48l2.83-2.83"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Micro-Commitments</h3>
        <p>Set tiny, specific goals like "10 pushups before 9am" or "read 10 pages." Small wins compound.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon purple">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Time-Boxed Goals</h3>
        <p>Choose 7, 14, 21, or 30 days. Finite feels achievable. Renew to continue.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon orange">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Live Activity Feed</h3>
        <p>See others complete in real-time. Their momentum becomes your motivation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"></path>
            <path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Smart Nudges</h3>
        <p>Get notified when your partner checks in. Reminders at your preferred time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon green">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"></circle>
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
            <line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
            <line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"></line>
            <line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"></line>
            <line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"></line>
            <line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"></line>
            <line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"></line>
            <line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Streak Tracking</h3>
        <p>Build and maintain streaks. Pause for illness or travel. 4-hour grace period.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon purple">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Reactions</h3>
        <p>Send quick reactions to celebrate completions. No awkward comments needed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon orange">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>18 Awards</h3>
        <p>Unlock achievements across 5 categories: Streaks, Comebacks, Consistency, Social, Proof.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"></path>
            <line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Comeback Tracking</h3>
        <p>Missed a few days? Track your comebacks. Rise stronger after breaks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon green">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>iOS Widgets</h3>
        <p>Track progress right from your home screen. Small, medium, and large widgets.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card reveal">
        <div class="feature-icon purple">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M20.24 12.24a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5 10.5V19h8.5z"></path>
            <line x1="16" y1="8" x2="2" y2="22"></line>
            <line x1="17.5" y1="15" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>XP & Levels</h3>
        <p>Earn experience points for check-ins, reactions, and achievements. Level up over time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-slow);
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    border-color: rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.1);
  }

  .feature-card.feature-large {
    grid-column: span 2;
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    padding: var(--space-8);
  }

  .feature-icon,
  .feature-icon-large {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.1), rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.05));
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--coral);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .feature-icon-large {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .feature-icon.green,
  .feature-icon-large.green {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.1), rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.05));
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .feature-icon.purple,
  .feature-icon-large.purple {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(148, 102, 222, 0.1), rgba(148, 102, 222, 0.05));
    color: var(--purple);
  }

  .feature-icon.orange {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 115, 46, 0.1), rgba(255, 115, 46, 0.05));
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .feature-content h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
  }

  .feature-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .feature-bullets {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .feature-bullets li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .feature-bullets li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--coral);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .feature-card.feature-large {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .feature-card.feature-large {
      grid-column: span 1;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
